body:
L1-HLT interface with seeding VETO  if algorithm bit is prescaled or masked.

This version uses the py example configuration work-around for upstream problems with Calo packer/unpacker sequence, pending fix.  Once the fix provided, the change is only in the example
configuration py files. 
Automatically ported from CMSSW_8_0_X #13340 (original by @cms-l1t-offline).
title: L1t hlt wseeds presc mask 80x
